title: Plat 5 Looking for good ranked team between gold+
body:
Hey guys, 

I'm Cooldudets and am currently plat 5 looking for a good ranked team to play with between gold and plat. I can play all roles but am best in mid, adc, and support. Someone please see this and add me as a friend in game (OCE server). My ign is Cooldudets (obviously) :p

I've been playing since season 2 so I have a lot of experience!
